    {
      "id": "P7T19ZFMUdT7d2CFP0spG",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 195,
      "y": 2488,
      "width": 876.8594360351562,
      "height": 200,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#f08c00",
      "backgroundColor": "#b2f2bb",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b0D",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1898881294,
      "version": 35,
      "versionNonce": 1122468878,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1780984943177,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "algoritm :\n\n\n1.  The first element in the array is assumed to be sorted. Take the second element and \nstore it separately in key \n\n    Compare key with the first element. If the first element is greater than key, \nthen key is placed in front of the first element.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "algoritm :\n\n\n1.  The first element in the array is assumed to be sorted. Take the second element and \nstore it separately in key \n\n    Compare key with the first element. If the first element is greater than key, \nthen key is placed in front of the first element.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "PpyGwvj0DmaF9Uc1UxeaH",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 189.99996948242188,
      "y": 2767.2000732421875,
      "width": 852.659423828125,
      "height": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#f08c00",
      "backgroundColor": "#b2f2bb",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b0G",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 317113102,
      "version": 98,
      "versionNonce": 813724370,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1780985031995,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "2.\nTake the third element and compare it with the elements on the left of it. \nPlaced it just behind the element smaller than it. If there is no element smaller than it,\n then place it at the beginning of the array.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "2.\nTake the third element and compare it with the elements on the left of it. \nPlaced it just behind the element smaller than it. If there is no element smaller than it,\n then place it at the beginning of the array.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "eqAXG4aNlvWkL6osgIuXM",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 190,
      "y": 2901,
      "width": 622.99951171875,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#f08c00",
      "backgroundColor": "#b2f2bb",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b0H",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1739553234,
      "version": 6,
      "versionNonce": 418322066,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1780985104644,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "3. Similarly, place every unsorted element at its correct position",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "3. Similarly, place every unsorted element at its correct position",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "mJOKvAwaup2RrmYkiTg8b",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 203.20001220703125,
      "y": 2997.5999755859375,
      "width": 382.25970458984375,
      "height": 425,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#b2f2bb",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b0I",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 249009742,
      "version": 293,
      "versionNonce": 1085415758,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1780985993795,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Void insertionSort ( inr arr[] , int size)\n{\n    for( i= 1 ; i<n ; i++)\n        {\n            key = arr[i]\n            j = i-1 \n        \n            while ( j > -1    A[j] > key)\n                {\n                     A[j+1] = A[j] \n                        j -- ;\n                }\n                \n            A [ j + 1] = key\n          }\n}\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Void insertionSort ( inr arr[] , int size)\n{\n    for( i= 1 ; i<n ; i++)\n        {\n            key = arr[i]\n            j = i-1 \n        \n            while ( j > -1    A[j] > key)\n                {\n                     A[j+1] = A[j] \n                        j -- ;\n                }\n                \n            A [ j + 1] = key\n          }\n}\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "CXN7aknOCEKovkrTonDfX",
