      "updated": 1780988774651,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Have we reached the end of any of the arrays?\n    No:\n        Compare current elements of both sub-arrays \n        Copy smaller element into sorted array\n        Move pointer of element containing smaller element\n    Yes:\n        Copy all remaining elements of non-empty array",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Have we reached the end of any of the arrays?\n    No:\n        Compare current elements of both sub-arrays \n        Copy smaller element into sorted array\n        Move pointer of element containing smaller element\n    Yes:\n        Copy all remaining elements of non-empty array",
